{"tid":2515441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3人旺角示威現場誤認便衣警 非法禁錮及非禮罪成 判囚10至15個月 官斥近乎「批鬥」","createTime":"2021-05-04T03:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T04:52:25.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0437105a7ec7d46bdef3e4152526ba4713f05d80","tid":2515441,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:53:51.000Z","msg":"3人旺角示威現場非法禁錮女子及非禮 判監10至15個月<br />\n<br />\n3人前年7月反修例遊行後在旺角聚集時，包圍一名被誤認為是便衣警察的女子，被控非法禁錮及參與非法集結，其中32歲任職廚師的被告黃子隆，被加控一項非禮罪，早上在區域法院判監1年3個月，至於其餘兩名被告，24歲社工吳睿哲判監1年，25歲女教師蘇瑋善就判監10個月。各人須向事主賠償1萬元。<br />\n<br />\n法官練錦鴻早前在裁決時指，受害人被強行留在現場、施襲及侮辱，過程接近「批鬥」，並將對執法人員不滿宣洩在受害人身上。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2390061\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2390061&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=a37c671c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2390061</a>"},{"pid":"b8ef79e6a32ecc564c5c71acdc21c6f873fc1637","tid":2515441,"uid":159271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe15027bd1754003884d3d9ad411f9803866e4a","tid":2515441,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"文革發動，批鬥重臨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSffqtxm1HzsfQCMY6yotMSJtWjQHiLtGSWNJgZFTpRpo?filename=PQqcoYF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQqcoYF.jpg&h=c19fcfa9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86c6c6a76149ebdfd025a6d5faffab7422736e42","tid":2515441,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"Cc toy 到而家都係會亂捉毛<br />\n永